===Pronoun===
'''ya'''

# (informal) [[you]]; used for writing or transcribing very informal speech peculiar to youthful speakers, typically containing many slang words
#: ''yo homes, smell ya later'' —[[w:Will Smith]], in the theme song to [[w:The Fresh Prince of Bel-Air]]

